## 📋 Testing Checklist

To manually verify the platform, follow this flow:

1. **Admin Verification:**
   - [ ] Log in with `admin@auto.com` / `admin123`.
   - [ ] Verify Dashboard loads statistics (initially mostly zeros).

2. **Customer Registration & Request:**
   - [ ] Open a new incognito window, click "Sign Up".
   - [ ] Register as a "Customer needing help".
   - [ ] Navigate to the "My Vehicles" tab and add a vehicle (e.g., Toyota Camry).
   - [ ] Click "New Request". Select your vehicle, enter a location, and describe a fake issue.
   - [ ] Verify the request appears under "My Requests" with a status of `PENDING`.

3. **Provider Registration & Job Acceptance:**
   - [ ] Open a third window/browser, click "Sign Up".
   - [ ] Register as a "Service Provider / Tow Truck" (Be sure to enter a Company Name).
   - [ ] Under "Find Jobs", verify you see the Customer's pending request.
   - [ ] Click "Accept Job". The request should disappear from "Find Jobs" and move to "My Active & Past Jobs" with status `ACCEPTED`.

4. **Lifecycle & Rating Completion:**
   - [ ] As the Provider, change the status to `IN_PROGRESS`.
   - [ ] Change the status to `COMPLETED`. When prompted, enter a final cost (e.g., 150).
   - [ ] Switch back to the Customer browser window and refresh.
   - [ ] The request should show `COMPLETED`. Click the 5-star rating scale to rate the provider.
   - [ ] Switch back to the Admin browser window. Verify the revenue, completed jobs count, and client counts have all updated.
